Super excited to partner with one of my favourite haircare brands Herbal Essences!!! If you follow my content you know that I’ve been using their products for a while now. I personally love and use two variants - ARGAN OIL OF MOROCCO and WHITE STRAWBERRY-SWEET MINT.  My hair texture is naturally dry and frizzy so the argan oil helps with that especially during the lockdown with all the DIY hair colouring & split ends since Im growing out my hair. I also have a flakey scalp so I use the strawberry & mint one twice a week for that. 

Im someone who likes to wash their hair daily and especially now with all the the extra house work and chores  I have to wash my hair before I go to bed. Im also someone that really likes to keep things simple, I air dry my hair, skip using conditioner  very often and basically break a lot of haircare rules 😜 But through all this I’ve pretty much just been using just these two products for the past few months  and I’ve been very happy with them.

Herbal Essences is enriched with real plant extracts, products include 90% naturally derived ingredients, is infused with antioxidants-aloe and sea kelp  its cruelty free, certified and verified by the oldest plant science organization in the world - Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew and the best part is all the variants smell divine .  You can find them on all leading e-commerce platforms - Flipkart, Nykaa and Amazon.
